---
title: Cheesy Garlic & Herb Chicken & Gnocchi Bake with Balsamic Pear Salad & Cheddar Cheese
description: Soft pillowy bundles of potato gnocchi and chicken bites, smothered in cheese and baked until deliciously golden and oozy. Now, if that hasn’t got your mouth watering, wait until you pull this dish of bubbling goodness from your oven in just 25 minutes.
